               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18311020-40-person353">
                  THOMAS 
                  DENT
               <interp inst="t18311020-40-person353" type="surname" value="DENT"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18311020-40-person353" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18311020-40-person353" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am pot-boy at the Cherry-tree public-house, Kingsland-road. On the afternoon of the 25th of July. I was opposite the prosecutor's shop; I saw the prisoner and another man in his shop- the prisoner took something from the shop, but I could not see what it was; he and the other man then ran away.</p>
               <p>
            
